  "instructions": [
    "Cut the corned beef into small cubes and set aside.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the garlic and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add the smoked paprika and chili powder and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the corned beef and cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the patatas bravas and cook for another 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in the chickpea flour and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Stir in the cilantro and lemon juice.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with red pepper flakes."
